2. **Team members install via uvx**

   ```bash
   uvx --from git+{{ 'ssh://git@github.company.com/eng/' if is_internal else 'https://github.com/username/' }}{{ script_name }} {{ script_name }}
   ```

3. **Add to Cursor config** (`~/.cursor/mcp.json`)

   ```json
